TEAGUE
v.
DOT. No. 281P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. John C. Hunter, for Joseph Teague, Jr. *199Tina Krasner, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st day of July 2006 by Petitioner to Supplement Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 17th day of August 2006."
